==Description==
{{FromGame}}
{{cquote2|This beautiful bird can be found in hot jungle climates where it expertly catches small insects for food. It is perhaps therefore ironic that it is usually caught for its bright plumage, which can be used in turn to make excellent fly fishing lures.|[[Bird book|William Oddity's Guide to the Avian]]}}

